vote.title: Approval and adoption of the Seventieth and Seventy-First Supplemental Concurrent Bond Ordinances amending the Master Bond Ordinance relating to Dallas Fort Worth International Airport (DFW) Joint Revenue Bonds, which will authorize the issuance of new debt not to exceed $3 billion for the period beginning March 1, 2025 and ending February 28, 2026, set parameters for bond sales, and authorize the use of bond proceeds to refund DFW’s outstanding commercial paper - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
